msg: Add code to read <requires> elements from WSDL and enable the test that ensure that mayProvides intents are matched between references and services.  This has implications for existing tests in that we now have to ensure that any mayProvides intent that is considered to be the default (a concept that the spec doesn't consider) is present in the intent list for the policy subject in question.
